Well you might have made an No-ip , but if you are on a router, type in ur url address bar, 192.168.1.1(well thats how i do it)
and login to your router, go to applications and gameing, and port forwarding, add the port 43594 to 43594 and enable it:P

And after u register a NO-IP wait like 10-15min for it to get settled.
